    <item>
      <title>法国债券收益率自 2007 年以来首次超过西班牙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/france-s-bond-yield-surpasses-spain-s-for-first-time-since-2007</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者质疑法国政府填补公共财政漏洞的能力，债券投资者自 2007 年以来首次要求持有法国债券的收益率高于评级较低的西班牙债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/france-s-bond-yield-surpasses-spain-s-for-first-time-since-2007</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 08:32:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
