      <title>沙特和利比亚有望增加石油供应，油价继续大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，沙特阿拉伯承诺在 12 月份增加产量，而利比亚各派达成协议，可能为恢复部分原油生产铺平道路，导致油价连续第二天下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-sept-26</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 23:30:50 GMT</pubDate>
